{"name":"Backstab","permission":{"default":0,"HehChXVvWoU0T1uV":3},"type":"ability","data":{"pattern":"white","requirements":"Assassin","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"description":"<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">An assassin may backstab as a thief. The assassin must attack from behind using Move Silently and Hide in Shadows. Under these conditions, the assassin attacks at +4 for double damage.</p>","save":""},"flags":{},"img":"/systems/ose/assets/default/ability.png","effects":[],"_id":"dD4xE5yY6E6yA7w"}
